Audit the following ETS stdlib code for thread safety. getInstance can be called concurrently from taskpool and EAWorker:

```ets
class Console {
  private static instance: Console | undefined = undefined

  public static getInstance(): Console {
    if (Console.instance == undefined) {
      Console.instance = new Console()
    }
    return Console.instance!
  }
}
```

